==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Introspective
<hw>In`tro*spec"tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>introspectif</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Inspecting within; seeing inwardly; capable of, or
exercising, inspection; self-conscious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Involving the act or results of conscious knowledge
of physical phenomena; -- contrasted with
<contr>associational</contr>.</def> <rj><au>J. S. Mill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Introsume</ent>⟦br⟧
